  <main class ="container ">
<h2 class="wiki title ">What is a watch-only wallet?</h2>

<div class="block ">
<div class="dot green"></div>
<div class="contentTitle ">Watch Wallet</div>
<div class="content ">
<div class="paragraph ">
Use
<span class="attentionText ">Watch Wallet</span>, users do not need to import private key, only need to enter wallet address, they can view all balances and transfer information under this address. </div>
<div class="paragraph ">Observation wallet can only view,
<span class="attentionText ">Cannot control wallet assets</span> and cannot transfer assets in the wallet. Only have
<span class="attentionText ">Private Keys</span>/
<span class="attentionText ">Mnemonics</span>/
<span class="attentionText ">Keystore (and the password corresponding to the keystore)</span> can really transfer the assets under the wallet.
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="block ">
<div class="dot green en"></div>
<div class="contentTitle ">Use</div>
<div class="content ">
<div class="paragraph ">
Using watch wallets to monitor assets is an effective and safe way to view wallet activity. You can use watch wallets when not trading and import them when you need to transfer assets
<span class="attentionText ">Private Keys</span>/
<span class="attentionText ">Mnemonics</span>/
<span class="attentionText ">Keystore</span>.
</div>
</div>
</div>

  <div class="block tips">
<div class="dot green en"></div>
<div class="contentTitle ">Tips</div>

<div class="content ">
<div class="paragraph ">
Only the address is uncontrollable! If you do not have <span class="attentionText ">private key</span>/
<span class="attentionText ">Mnemonics</span>/
<span class="attentionText ">Keystore (and password corresponding to keystore)</span>, please don't transfer money inside!
</div>

<div class="paragraph ">
Thanks to Ethereum's transparent disclosure, anyone with your address can find information on funds and transactions at your address. Although only the address does not control assets, it is easy to disclose your asset information. If you have a large amount of assets, please keep it in a safe place. Do not disclose the address to others.
</div>
</div>
</div>
